# Backup files written by scripts/correction_miner.py during prompt
# promotion. The miner copies the existing prompt into a sibling
# ``backups/`` directory before overwriting; these are ephemeral
# rollback artifacts and must never enter source control. The bare
# filename pattern is kept as defense-in-depth in case a future change
# accidentally re-targets the prompts directory itself.
backups/
meeting_minutes_llm_backup_*.md
